{
  "stem": "11089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because of money, he saved lots of Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarians looked away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I said, in the beginning, we delivered them to Budapest and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We saved as much as we can, as many as we can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in 19-- in March, end of March, April beginning-- the Germans came in, and my father couldn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of those Hungarians went and told about him, what he did all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they came and they took him away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Hungarians took away to the Germans, to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was the first transport with Hungarian Jews to go to the camps, not knowing where they're going.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we-- he had some knowledge because in 1941, my [NON-ENGLISH], Nathan was taken away with his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, where I was with my mother, the owner of that property, he was a [NON-ENGLISH] The committee of the Jews was outside the city.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow, a little card arrived to their office from my father, from somewhere from Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember, he assembled us as a ghetto, and he read the little card.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my father wrote the following, [NON-ENGLISH] which means, I was-- I went to see my father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I couldn't find him, but it's very hot over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's like fire.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the word fire was mentioned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hot over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started to speculate, what does he means?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went to see my [NON-ENGLISH], his father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't find him, and it's boiling over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Still, no one believed what that hot means, what the fire means.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all knew we're going to be resettled into Hungary to go to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's when we started to realize what's happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
